title: [+ year +]년 [? if z_party_name != "CVP": <span style="color: #000000;">중앙당</span>?][? if z_party_name == "CVP": <span style="color: #000000;">**CVP**</span>?] 회의
subtitle: [+ z_leader +]는 반-후겐베르크 우파와 합당하기 위해 움직입니다...
view-if: stegerwald_skibidi_time == time and (z_leader == "Stegerwald" or z_leader == "Adenauer") and dnvp_ideology == "Radical" and not kvp_cnblp_sister and not dkp_merger_waiting
new-page: true
max-visits: 1
